	(text_box "Place the TMP119 physically close to the flash storage chip\nIdeally within a few millimeters on the same PCB side.\n\nAvoid thermal vias directly under the TMP119. Use a solid copper reference plane to allow the sensor to track the flash package temperature rather than localized PCB heating."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 89.408 161.29 0)
		(size 53.34 20.32)
		(margins 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525)
		(stroke
			(width 0)
			(type solid)
		)
		(fill
